import React from 'react';
import { Box, Flex, Image, Button, Heading, Spacer } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import logo from '../images/logo.png'; // using images with import

function NavBar() {
    return (
      <Flex
        w='100%'
        pt='25px'
        pb='25px'
        pr='105px'
        pl='105px'
        // alignItems='center'
      >
          <Box display="flex" alignItems="center">
            <Image width="100px" height="100px" src={logo} alt="test"/>
            <Heading as='h1' size='2xl'> IOU </Heading>
          </Box>
          <Spacer />
          <Box>
            <Button colorScheme='teal' variant='link'>Overview</Button>
            <Button colorScheme='teal' variant='link'>Features</Button>
            <Button colorScheme='teal' variant='link'>About</Button>
            <Button colorScheme='teal' variant='link'>Contact Us</Button>
          </Box>
          <Spacer />
          <Box>
            <Button colorScheme='teal' variant='outline'>Log In</Button>
            <Button colorScheme='teal' variant='outline'>Sign Up</Button>
          </Box>
      </Flex>
    );
  }
  
export default NavBar;
